"""
Weather ML Pipeline
====================
Train on up to 6 CSV files, then analyze any test CSV to compute:
  - Heat Index
  - Wind Chill
  - Comfort Index
  - Rain Probability  (Random Forest classifier)
  - Pressure Trend
  - Condition Rating

Usage
-----
  python weather_ml_pipeline.py \
      --train  data1.csv data2.csv data3.csv \
      --test   new_data.csv \
      --output results/

Dependencies
------------
  pip install pandas numpy scikit-learn imbalanced-learn joblib matplotlib
"""

